the process authority. Failure to have 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
documentation that the pasteurization 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
equipment will achieve its goals will violate 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
21 CFR 123.8 and will mean that the product 
