that are occurring for those key aspect of 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
the process identified by the process 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
authority in section 4.b.1.ii of this 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Appendix. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=73 g=1 f=1 -->
5. Container Integrity Critical Controls Points 
